    "MEVA comprises more than 9300 h of continuous uncut video that contains spontaneous background activity.",
    "In this dataset, there are 37 kinds of actions, spanning 144 h in total, and actors and props are framed with borders.",
    "In addition, about 100 actors were gathered to perform scripted scenes and spontaneous background activities in a gated and controlled venue over three weeks, and video was collected in various ways so that indoor and outdoor views overlapped or did not overlap.",
